Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:38.93,0:01:42.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这样晚餐的材料就全部买齐了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:42.70,0:01:43.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,接下来是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:52.98,0:01:54.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好漂亮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:56.18,0:01:57.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,旅行啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:58.18,0:02:00.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果能有时间跟薰一起去的话…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:01.02,0:02:05.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就可以跟薰一起看这样漂亮的景色了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:10.19,0:02:16.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第七话  幻妖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:17.77,0:02:20.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我到底在做什么啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:20.94,0:02:22.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,带这种东西回来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:25.47,0:02:27.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:27.58,0:02:29.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一定有时间能够跟薰一起…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:30.98,0:02:33.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就找房东跟管理员一起去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:33.75,0:02:34.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗯 这样也不错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:35.18,0:02:37.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊 咦 那个…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:38.42,0:02:39.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我回来了 小葵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:40.66,0:02:41.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,欢迎大家回来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:42.59,0:02:43.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,回来的相当早呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:44.49,0:02:48.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗯 碰巧我们三个下午都停课
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:49.33,0:02:50.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂 房东
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:51.17,0:02:52.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一起去温泉吧 温泉…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:53.00,0:02:55.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,温泉…吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:03.25,0:03:06.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哇啊 山上的空气真新鲜啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:08.48,0:03:09.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,终于到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:10.32,0:03:11.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:11.82,0:03:12.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,请等我一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:13.26,0:03:14.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妙子？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:14.59,0:03:17.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,请等我一…下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:21.66,0:03:23.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你还好吧 妙子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:24.77,0:03:25.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:26.27,0:03:27.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这种事我已经习惯了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:28.14,0:03:29.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊勒？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:29.47,0:03:30.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,买来当做午餐的车站便当呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:31.31,0:03:33.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:37.98,0:03:39.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对不起 对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:40.15,0:03:41.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,人家很期待的说…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:42.15,0:03:45.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没办法啦 忘记便当的事 去哪里吃午餐吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:46.06,0:03:47.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真的很对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:47.72,0:03:49.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,打起精神来啦 妙子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:50.26,0:03:53.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再怎么说 今天可是摄影社的新人欢迎合宿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:53.73,0:03:55.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妙子你可是主角啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.00,0:03:57.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:57.57,0:03:59.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那个…你们…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:00.34,0:04:01.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎么了吗？小葵？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:02.54,0:04:04.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真的可以吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.21,0:04:07.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,像我这样毫无关系的人也跟来…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:07.81,0:04:10.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没关系没关系 别在意这种小事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.88,0:04:13.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且基本上是我硬拉你来的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:14.55,0:04:15.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没错没错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:15.88,0:04:17.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,尤其是个美人就更欢迎了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.99,0:04:19.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真羡慕你啊 花菱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:20.32,0:04:22.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这么漂亮的人居然是你的房东
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:23.26,0:04:25.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这样啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:25.66,0:04:27.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原来其他人看起来就是这种感觉啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.43,0:04:31.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是的 大家都太会奉承了啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.94,0:04:38.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,空气真的很新鲜呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.54,0:04:41.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雅要是能一起来就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.48,0:04:45.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对啊 但是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:45.61,0:04:49.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,明天的旅行 我打算陪葵大小姐一起去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:51.05,0:04:55.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是因为工作 无论如何都只能放弃了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.89,0:04:57.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也就是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:58.46,0:05:02.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,葵大小姐的事…就务必务必请你仔细的照顾了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:03.07,0:05:04.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,薰…少…爷…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:04.73,0:05:08.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要是…万一葵大小姐发生什么的话…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:09.61,0:05:12.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好像如果发生什么事就要把我杀了一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.54,0:05:15.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,话说回来 小妙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:16.21,0:05:18.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到底还要多久才会到旅馆？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.78,0:05:19.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这…这个…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:20.38,0:05:22.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是就在车站的附近而已吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:22.72,0:05:23.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,车站？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:24.05,0:05:25.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,车站的话大概…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:25.95,0:05:28.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在那附近吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:30.89,0:05:33.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对不起 因为我是路痴…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:35.33,0:05:36.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,饶了我们吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:36.80,0:05:39.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道地点的只有预约的水无月你啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.00,0:05:42.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,叫万叶苑的旅馆…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.11,0:05:44.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那个…那个…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.11,0:05:46.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊 我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:46.51,0:05:47.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这边
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:47.68,0:05:49.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,走这边的话就是近路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:55.45,0:05:57.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对不起 是这边才对
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:00.62,0:06:01.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,完成
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:02.96,0:06:04.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,猴子先生 猴子先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.23,0:06:06.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大概…在这边
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:11.63,0:06:12.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一加一是？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:12.97,0:06:13.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,二
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:14.77,0:06:16.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这…这边呢…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:18.11,0:06:19.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,呜…不要啦…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:24.18,0:06:26.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们要投宿的旅馆到底在哪？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:27.45,0:06:29.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,从开始已经找了三小时了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:30.29,0:06:31.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:33.29,0:06:34.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小葵 你还好吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:35.96,0:06:37.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,谢谢你的关心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:37.86,0:06:39.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我没问题的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:40.40,0:06:41.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这样…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:43.47,0:06:46.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小葵她看起来虽然很瘦小
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:47.04,0:06:49.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也许其实是个很坚强的女孩呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:50.24,0:06:54.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对不起 对不起 全部都是我不好啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:54.68,0:06:56.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妙子 借我一下…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:56.75,0:06:59.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,车站是这里 然后这里是大街
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:59.95,0:07:02.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,然后隔壁的旅馆是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:10.13,0:07:12.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一时间还反应不过来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:12.80,0:07:15.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不管怎样 能找到旅馆真是太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:16.20,0:07:17.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是 都精疲力尽了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:18.03,0:07:20.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,早点去泡温泉消除疲劳吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:20.87,0:07:21.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,咦…？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:22.44,0:07:24.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,『没有』是什么意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.67,0:07:28.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也就是说今天并没有接受那样的预约
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:28.61,0:07:29.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎么会那样？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:30.35,0:07:31.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我确实有预约到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.51,0:07:34.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,明立大学 摄影社…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.08,0:07:36.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就算这样说…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:37.52,0:07:40.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,难道说小妙你预约到下个月的不成？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:41.69,0:07:42.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂 蒂娜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.26,0:07:46.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就算是妙子也不可能会…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:46.46,0:07:47.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊 找到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:48.10,0:07:50.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在明年的今天有预约
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:51.77,0:07:53.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎么这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:54.10,0:07:56.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那个 还有空的房间吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:56.97,0:07:59.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这个旺季房间全部都满了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:59.44,0:08:01.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很不巧也没有取消订房的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:02.44,0:08:03.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,难道不能通融一下吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:04.58,0:08:06.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就算您怎么说也…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:08.02,0:08:08.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,薰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:10.69,0:08:11.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,葵大小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:12.35,0:08:15.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果发生什么事的话 请用这个VIP卡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:16.26,0:08:20.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大部分的企业应该都能通用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:22.93,0:08:23.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:24.77,0:08:25.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎么这样啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:26.37,0:08:27.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那个…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:28.24,0:08:31.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不管什么样的房间都没关系 拜托你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:31.91,0:08:33.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因为房间真的满…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:35.51,0:08:37.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这…这是？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:38.48,0:08:40.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你 快点准备房间
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.98,0:08:42.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是房间都满了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:42.58,0:08:43.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没关系 快点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:43.65,0:08:44.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是…是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:46.26,0:08:47.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是非常抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:48.82,0:08:51.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,现在马上为您准备好房间
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:52.16,0:08:53.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,非常谢谢你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:54.50,0:08:55.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小葵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:56.16,0:08:57.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是太好了呢 薰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:59.10,0:09:00.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,谢谢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:00.77,0:09:01.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,各位
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.14,0:09:04.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,别呆坐着了 小葵帮我们说情了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:05.14,0:09:06.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:06.41,0:09:07.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,非常谢谢你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:08.24,0:09:10.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是厉害啊 房东
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:10.75,0:09:11.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没什么啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:12.41,0:09:15.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因为今天是跟薰第一次的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:19.82,0:09:23.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊啊…极乐极乐…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:23.93,0:09:27.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,流了一身汗后泡个温泉真是特别舒服呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:29.00,0:09:31.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我真是的…我真是的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:32.00,0:09:33.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎么了吗？妙子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:35.37,0:09:36.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,葵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:36.87,0:09:39.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我真的老是把事情搞砸对吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:39.71,0:09:41.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我总是只会为周围的人带来麻烦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:43.38,0:09:44.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今天也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:45.15,0:09:48.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我一定是做什么事情都不行的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:49.32,0:09:50.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没有这回事喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:51.22,0:09:52.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妙子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:52.72,0:09:53.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,葵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:54.22,0:09:58.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只要努力的话 一定会有认同你努力的人在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:59.00,0:10:00.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妙子你有 我也有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:01.50,0:10:05.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以我总是想着那个人然后努力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:06.50,0:10:09.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只要想起那个人高兴的脸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:09.87,0:10:11.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,即使是很幸苦也会持续努力下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:12.54,0:10:13.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:14.04,0:10:15.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妙子也请你努力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:16.11,0:10:17.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你做得到的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:17.81,0:10:19.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因为我也做到了 我会为你打气的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:21.22,0:10:22.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,非常谢谢你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:23.39,0:10:25.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,气氛别弄得那么苦闷嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:26.96,0:10:28.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这可是难得的合宿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:29.13,0:10:31.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就放下一切好好的玩嘛 对吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:32.90,0:10:33.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:34.66,0:10:38.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,来吧 春季合宿例行的宴会 宴会
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:40.30,0:10:41.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等很久了吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:43.71,0:10:44.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,已经开始了喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:45.61,0:10:47.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,外国女孩穿浴衣看起来也很不错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:48.44,0:10:49.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果只是看起来…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:51.18,0:10:53.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好痛 对不起我迟到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:54.72,0:10:56.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好厉害的声音
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:56.69,0:10:59.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,的确 比外国人的蒂娜还大呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:05.73,0:11:06.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,让你们久等了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:07.83,0:11:08.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好美…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:09.13,0:11:10.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好可爱…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:11.97,0:11:13.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,让我们再次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:13.80,0:11:16.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为明立大学摄影社的再次出发
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:16.77,0:11:18.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,干杯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:31.35,0:11:32.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那个 水无月同学
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:34.36,0:11:35.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎么了？社长
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:36.79,0:11:39.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,现在有个重大的任务要交给你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:40.53,0:11:41.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,重大的任务？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:45.37,0:11:46.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,先看看这个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:49.41,0:11:50.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:59.52,0:12:01.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这…这是什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:02.29,0:12:05.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是我跟佐藤在一年级的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:05.52,0:12:07.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,靠着努力与根性所拍摄到的鬼火
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:08.73,0:12:09.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也就是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:10.79,0:12:11.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,灵异照片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:12.20,0:12:13.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,灵…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:14.30,0:12:16.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我现在要告诉你一个地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:18.03,0:12:18.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那就是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:19.30,0:12:22.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在这后山约一公里处的小祠堂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:22.57,0:12:24.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在森林深处的那座祠堂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:24.91,0:12:27.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在这一带也是十分有名的灵异地点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:28.24,0:12:29.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只要去就一定会出现
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:30.08,0:12:31.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是这么样的一个地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:31.78,0:12:35.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,新社员是一定要去那儿拍张灵异照片回来的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:36.02,0:12:37.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这就是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:37.59,0:12:39.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,明立大学摄影社春季合宿的惯例
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:39.86,0:12:41.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,试胆摄影大会！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:42.02,0:12:43.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,然后这次是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:43.79,0:12:45.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,水无月 轮到你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:46.93,0:12:47.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,先跟你说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:48.43,0:12:49.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这是我们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:50.03,0:12:53.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,还有花菱跟蒂娜都参加过的例行活动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:53.77,0:12:57.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以 这是绝对无法拒绝的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:04.25,0:13:06.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我绝对不会再拍第二次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:06.52,0:13:07.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,别想落跑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:13.59,0:13:14.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哇…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:15.26,0:13:17.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好棒的例行活动啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:17.79,0:13:20.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我最喜欢那种超自然的东西了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:21.10,0:13:21.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,水无月同学
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:22.43,0:13:24.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你真的明白这活动的主旨吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:24.87,0:13:27.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是的 只要拍幽灵回来就可以了对吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:28.30,0:13:29.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我会加油的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:33.14,0:13:35.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那么 我去啰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:37.48,0:13:38.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,加油啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:39.42,0:13:44.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,男人跟女人的欢迎会
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:45.49,0:13:50.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是18岁 而我19
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:53.43,0:13:54.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妙子她…没问题吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:56.03,0:13:58.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗯 我想是没问题的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:59.54,0:14:02.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对不起 因为我是路痴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:04.41,0:14:05.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,该不会…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:08.98,0:14:09.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,薰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:12.65,0:14:14.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你要去找妙子对吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:14.85,0:14:15.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:15.99,0:14:17.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也请让我一起去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:17.85,0:14:18.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,耶？可是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:19.32,0:14:22.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拜托你 我也很担心妙子…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:24.03,0:14:26.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小葵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:29.27,0:14:30.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是暗啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:31.17,0:14:32.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小葵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:32.50,0:14:34.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,绝对不可以离开我的身边
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:36.91,0:14:37.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:38.81,0:14:39.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妙子…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:40.31,0:14:41.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妙子…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:42.04,0:14:43.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妙子…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:44.21,0:14:46.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妙子…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:06.77,0:15:08.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,开始起风了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:09.14,0:15:11.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且雾也慢慢…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:13.98,0:15:16.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原来是鸟啊 吓了一跳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:18.08,0:15:20.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要是只有一个人来可能很糟糕吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:21.22,0:15:23.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哈哈 没事吧？小葵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:25.49,0:15:26.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我没事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:27.22,0:15:28.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,赶快走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:28.99,0:15:32.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想妙子现在自己一个人一定很不安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:33.73,0:15:35.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗯 也对
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:36.23,0:15:39.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好厉害 小葵对这种事情不会害怕啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:44.87,0:15:45.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:46.11,0:15:47.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妙子呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:47.61,0:15:48.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妙子…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:49.88,0:15:50.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妙子…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:51.28,0:15:53.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妙子…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:55.45,0:15:57.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,会不会在祠堂里面？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:57.95,0:15:58.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:05.56,0:16:06.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不在啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:07.83,0:16:09.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到哪里去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:09.73,0:16:10.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,薰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:11.67,0:16:12.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那个是？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:18.98,0:16:20.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,出现了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:26.98,0:16:29.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊勒？这不是学长吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:30.72,0:16:32.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你们在这种地方做什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:34.39,0:16:35.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妙子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:37.39,0:16:38.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是这样啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:39.46,0:16:41.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那个 你没事吗？妙子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:42.57,0:16:43.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有没有哪里受伤…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:44.23,0:16:44.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:45.30,0:16:47.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我完全热衷在拍照片上面了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:47.64,0:16:49.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没想到时间已经经过那么久…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:50.17,0:16:52.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我完全没有注意到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:53.68,0:16:55.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这样啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:56.45,0:16:57.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:57.95,0:16:59.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我好像又给大家添麻烦了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:00.38,0:17:01.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,总之没事就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:02.55,0:17:03.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,已经拍好了吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:04.79,0:17:06.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,差不多也该回旅馆去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:09.06,0:17:10.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好浓的雾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:12.13,0:17:13.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,伤脑筋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:13.80,0:17:15.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这样就几乎看不见了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:15.90,0:17:16.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没问题啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:17.47,0:17:18.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到旅馆几乎就是一直线的路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:19.80,0:17:23.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不 我认为还是等到雾散了比较好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:23.84,0:17:26.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,路上也有断崖或是河川之类的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:27.61,0:17:29.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要是不小心迷路的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:29.68,0:17:31.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,说不定会发生意外的不是吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:32.21,0:17:33.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,说的也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:34.05,0:17:35.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等到雾散吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:35.85,0:17:38.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,蒂娜她们 如果不会太担心就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:46.80,0:17:49.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊勒？妙子睡着了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:49.80,0:17:51.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因为太累的关系吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:52.37,0:17:54.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗯 好像是那样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:56.27,0:17:57.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊勒？会冷吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:57.91,0:18:01.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是…一安心下来就突然…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:02.51,0:18:03.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,耶？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:03.85,0:18:05.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,其实 其实…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:06.22,0:18:09.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到达这里之前我一直都很害怕的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:09.69,0:18:11.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为什么要那么勉强？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:12.05,0:18:17.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因为…能够和薰一起旅行是我的梦想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:18.36,0:18:19.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这样啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:20.86,0:18:22.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小葵之所以看起来坚强
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:23.20,0:18:25.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,并不是因为她本身就是勇敢的女孩子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:25.53,0:18:27.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只是不想让我担心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:28.17,0:18:29.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以在勉强自己
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:30.27,0:18:32.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,其实真正的小葵她…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:32.68,0:18:34.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没事了 不用担心了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:35.51,0:18:36.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:44.09,0:18:45.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎…怎么办…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:46.26,0:18:47.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,颤抖停不下来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:50.19,0:18:51.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小葵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:51.43,0:18:52.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:56.87,0:18:58.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,薰？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:59.07,0:19:00.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不会再发抖了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:05.91,0:19:10.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是的 停下来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:25.93,0:19:27.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,薰？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:30.03,0:19:31.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊 小葵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:37.74,0:19:39.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,早安 来这里看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:41.74,0:19:42.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:50.59,0:19:51.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这里…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:52.49,0:19:54.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗯 很漂亮吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:55.99,0:19:58.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是的 很漂亮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:02.93,0:20:04.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,又一个梦想实现了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:05.43,0:20:06.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,耶？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:06.77,0:20:07.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:08.47,0:20:09.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:13.98,0:20:15.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那个 薰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:16.41,0:20:19.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可以再带我到别的地方去吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:19.88,0:20:20.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗯？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:21.72,0:20:23.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我…是第一次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:24.32,0:20:26.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,像这样子出来旅行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:26.89,0:20:27.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可以啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:28.32,0:20:31.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,摄影社除了合宿之外也有其他摄影活动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:32.90,0:20:33.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:34.40,0:20:36.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那个…下次两个人一起…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:37.90,0:20:40.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,说的也是 下次两个人一起吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:41.04,0:20:41.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:42.44,0:20:43.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,差不多也该回去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:43.87,0:20:44.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,叫妙子起床
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:45.44,0:20:46.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,蒂娜她们也在等我们吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:47.31,0:20:48.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,来 走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:52.78,0:20:54.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,学长…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:55.32,0:20:55.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我成功了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:56.62,0:20:57.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,清楚的拍到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:58.39,0:20:59.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很多幽灵呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:00.22,0:21:01.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,开玩笑的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:02.06,0:21:03.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎么了吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:03.99,0:21:06.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊 那个…大致上…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:06.73,0:21:08.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,跟我们比较起来是还差很多
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:08.73,0:21:11.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是你对摄影的热诚倒是可以认同
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:11.83,0:21:14.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,希望你以后要更加强自己的摄影技术
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:14.44,0:21:15.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,成为了不起的摄影员
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:16.37,0:21:17.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:17.61,0:21:19.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今后我也会继续努力
