Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:48.23,0:21:53.14,SongRom,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\ko20\2a&Hff&}{\ko20}a {\ko20}na {\ko20}ta {\ko30}no {\ko90}koe {\ko30}de{\ko30} {\ko30}ki {\ko30}ki {\ko30}ta {\ko60}ku {\ko30}te
